      Methods in com.vmware.nsx.model that return Icon.Builder 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Icon.Builder Icon.Builder.setPlacement(java.lang.String placement)
      Possible values are: Icon.PLACEMENT_PRE, Icon.PLACEMENT_POST, If specified as PRE, the icon appears before the UI element.

      Multi-line text to be shown on tooltip while hovering over the icon.

      Possible values are: Icon.TYPE_ERROR, Icon.TYPE_WARNING, Icon.TYPE_INFO, Icon.TYPE_INPROGRESS, Icon.TYPE_SUCCESS, Icon.TYPE_DETAIL, Icon.TYPE_NOT_AVAILABLE, Icon.TYPE_SECURITY, Icon.TYPE_NETWORKING, Icon.TYPE_LOAD_BALANCER, Icon.TYPE_VPN, Icon.TYPE_DOMAIN, Icon.TYPE_GROUP, Icon.TYPE_DISTRIBUTED_FIREWALL, Icon.TYPE_NETWORKING_TIER0, Icon.TYPE_NETWORKING_TIER1, Icon.TYPE_SEGMENT, Icon.TYPE_SYSTEM, Icon.TYPE_SYSTEM_FABRIC, Icon.TYPE_SYSTEM_BACKUPRESTORE, Icon.TYPE_INVENTORY_GROUPS, Icon.TYPE_SECURITY_DFW, Icon will be rendered based on its type.
